Miki Hood https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Miki_Hood 0 Barbara Mary "Miki" Hood (9 January 1915 – September, 1994) was an English stage and film actress. She played the female lead in the 1934 film Guest of Honour. Barbara_Mary_"_Miki_"_Hood ( 9_January_1915 – September , 1994 ) was an_English_stage_and_film_actress .
